import React from "react";
import { Col, Row, Form, FormGroup, Label, Button, ModalBody, ModalFooter,Input } from "reactstrap";
import Translate from "../../Translate";
import jwt from "jwt-simple";

const AddContact = ({ id, props }) => {

    let firstname, lastname, username, password, position, active;
    let user = props.user[0]
    console.log(props.user)
    return (
        <React.Fragment>
            <Form
                onSubmit={e => {
                    e.preventDefault();
                    if (!firstname.value.trim() || !username.value.trim() || !password.value.trim()) {
                        return;
                    }
                    props.addUser({
                        firstname:firstname.value,
                        lastname:lastname.value,
                        username:username.value,
                        password:jwt.encode("",password.value),
                        position:0,
                        active:0
                    });
                    firstname.value = "";
                    lastname.value = "";
                    username.value = "";
                    password.value = "";
                    position.value = "";
                    active.value = "";
                }}
            >
                <ModalBody>
                    <Row>
                        <Col md={6}>
                            <FormGroup>
                                <Label for="firstName"><Translate name="firstname"/></Label>
                                <input
                                    className="form-control"
                                    type="text"
                                    name="firstname"
                                    id="firstName"
                                    ref={node => (firstname = node)}
                                    value={user.firstname?user.firstname:""}
                                    required
                                />
                            </FormGroup>
                        </Col>
                        <Col md={6}>
                            <FormGroup>
                                <Label for="lastName"><Translate name="lastname"/></Label>
                                <input
                                    className="form-control"
                                    type="text"
                                    name="lastname"
                                    id="lastName"
                                    ref={node => (lastname = node)}
                                />
                            </FormGroup>
                        </Col>
                    </Row>
                    <Row>
                        <Col md={6}>
                            <FormGroup>
                                <Label for="username"><Translate name="username"/></Label>
                                <input
                                    className="form-control"
                                    type="text"
                                    name="username"
                                    id="username"
                                    ref={node => (username = node)}
                                    required
                                />
                            </FormGroup>
                        </Col>
                        <Col md={6}>
                            <FormGroup>
                                <Label for="password"><Translate name="password"/></Label>
                                <input
                                    className="form-control"
                                    type="password"
                                    name="password"
                                    id="password"
                                    ref={node => (password = node)}
                                    required
                                />
                            </FormGroup>
                        </Col>
                    </Row>
                    <Row>
                        <Col md={6}>
                            <FormGroup>
                                <Label for="position"><Translate name="position"/></Label>
                                <Input type="select" id="position" name="position" ref={node => (position = node)} >
                                    {props.positions.map((item, key)=>{
                                        return <option value={item.id} key={key}>{item.name}</option>
                                    })}
                                </Input>
                            </FormGroup>
                        </Col>
                        <Col md={6}>
                            <FormGroup>
                                <Label for="active"><Translate name="active"/></Label>
                                <Input type="select" id="active" name="active" ref={node => (active = node)} >
                                    <option value="0">Այո</option>
                                    <option value="1">Ոչ</option>
                                </Input>
                            </FormGroup>
                        </Col>
                    </Row>

                </ModalBody>
                <ModalFooter>
                    <Button color="primary" type="submit">
                        <Translate name="add"/>
                    </Button>
                </ModalFooter>
            </Form>
        </React.Fragment>
    );
};

export default AddContact;
